snippet.title: DRAGON BALL: Sparking! ZERO - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
And just like that, the spark ignites… again. 💥 DRAGON BALL: Sparking! ZERO is coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X | S, and PC on October 10th at 3pm PT | 6pm ET.
